            <note xml:id="n03010401" n="1">If this was <name type="person" key="Robertson, John">Corporal John Robinson</name> (<name type="person" key="Robertson, John">Robertson</name>), we may have the reason for his reduction to private. See above, <ref n="1803-12-26" type="related">December 26, 1803</ref>. <name type="person" key="Warfington, Richard">Corporal Warfington</name> seems to have retained the confidence of his superiors, suggesting that he was not the corporal concerned here.</note>
